"<subscript>x</subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-"
"t<superscript>2</superscript>) dt"
msgstr ""
"Komplementäre Fehlerfunktion erfc(x) = 1 - erf(x) = 2/&radic;&pi; &int;"
"<subscript>x</subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-"
"t<superscript>2</superscript>) dt"

